{"tid":1426470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有藍絲廢老屈人搶錢","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:41:37.000Z","uid":200575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"398293fe1c50d4c7fc6c641d564a071769d9832a","tid":1426470,"uid":200575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"冇得fact check,我冇辦法搶佢部手機黎cap圖比你地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公司有廢老周圍同人講,<br />\n話有好多黑衣人圍係ATM附近,<br />\n兇人唔比人㩒錢,㩒左錢既會比黑衣人搶錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有同事問佢真唔真<br />\n佢話佢朋友whatsapp send比佢既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前不合作活動個陣又講過類似既<br />\n話有班黑衣人企係月台<br />\n強迫落車既乘客同媒體講支持佢地既活動<br />\n<br />\n其他廢老信到十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇辦法正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過同佢地講過唔係咁<br />\n佢地唔撚信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5295e4ba7a29cf061c890858749fcd79cadf7436","tid":1426470,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"*变種行劫*<br />\n<br />\n初在旺角區發生，幾十個黑衣曱甴圍住櫃員機向㩒完錢既市民攞義助，市民見啲曱甴人多武力展示又無法脱身，焗住俾一百幾十佢地，如果唔俾真係唔知發生咩事。(以上過程屬於行劫)<br />\n<br />\n跟住其他地區，都有以上同類事件發生。<br />\n<br />\n*ATM机撳錢之前及期間要小心留意四週環境！！*<br />\n<br />\n呢段呀麻"},{"pid":"383f71130ac83799117d844eb365a7f35fda9f67","tid":1426470,"uid":24704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109c9